<HEADLINE> Over 1,000 Excellent Workers, Units to Be Cited </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 21 (Xinhua) -- One thousand model workers across
the country and 300 advanced working units will receive top honors
for their achievements.
</P>
<P>
