Medal, and outstanding groups will get a "May 1" certificate of
merit.
</P>
<P>
Over half of the 1,000 workers are employed in grassroots-level
positions. Scientific researchers and technicians account for 15.3
percent of those receiving citations; factory leaders and company
managers make up another 10.5 percent.
</P>
<P>
