organization hopes that workers nationwide will be encouraged to
contribute to the realization of the Ninth Five-Year Plan
(1996-2000) and the country's trans-century development goals.
</P>
<P>
Model working units and their managers have passed examinations
by departments of industry and commerce, taxation, auditing, and
discipline inspection.
