humanitarian workers and I urge all the parties to stop the
fighting and allow the unimpeded delivery of humanitarian
assistance to the civilian population caught in the conflict," the
statement said.
</P>
<P>
Annan paid tribute to the courage of all the aid workers who,
he said, "in spite of extremely difficult conditions, are doing
their utmost to deliver assistance to the population in need."
</P>
<P>
He hoped repatriation and air-bridge operations will start very
soon to save the lives of the vulnerable women and children
needing better care. 
