<HEADLINE> Xishuangban'na Border Trade Fair Ends </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUNMING, April 22 (Xinhua) -- A border trade fair in southwest
China came to an end on April 20, with transactions totaling more
than 200 million yuan.
</P>
<P>
Attending the event, the first Langcang River-Mekong River
Sub-Regional Economic Cooperation Xishuangban'na Border Trade
Fair, were more than 2,600 businessmen from 20 Chinese provinces,
