developing the sub-regional economic cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Xishuangban'na is located at the juncture between China and
other countries in the area. The fair will become an annual event,
according to Dao Aimin, commissioner of the Xishuangban'na Dai
Nationality Autonomous Prefecture. 
