Kazakhstan and their neighbors will not only benefit the good
neighborly friendship and mutual beneficial cooperation between
China and Kazakhstan, but also has great significance for the
maintenance of peace in the Asia-Pacific region and the world as a
whole.
</P>
<P>
During his visit to Kazakhstan in 1994, Li and President
Nursultan Abishevich Nazarbayev signed an agreement concerning the
borders between the two countries. China, Kazakhstan, Russia,
Kirghizstan and Tadzhikistan signed an agreement on confidence
building in military fields in border areas last April.
</P>
