agreement soon.
</P>
<P>
He pointed out that in recent years, China's National People's
Congress (NPC) and the parliament of Kazakhstan have forged sound
cooperative relations, which plays an important role in the
bilateral relations.
</P>
<P>
He said he wishes that the two countries will maintain the
positive momentum of bilateral relations and continue to
contribute to the development of the friendship and good
neighborly and two-way cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Ospanov said that he is deeply impressed with China's reform,
opening up and economic development, and wishes that the bilateral
relations should be further strengthened in order to promote trade
between the two countries that will benefit both sides.  
