<HEADLINE> Venezuela to Reinforce War Against Drugs </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CARACAS, April 21 (Xinhua) -- Venezuela will intensify its war
against drug-related crimes by reinforcing the National Anti-Drug
Command of the National Guard.
</P>
<P>
A national information network will be set up to enable the
anti-drug command to combat drug trafficking more efficiently,
commander of the National Guard, General Euro Rincon Viloria, said
today.
</P>
<P>
