Minister Pedro Nicolas Valencia Vivas.
</P>
<P>
They reportedly analyzed the evolution of the case of Justo
Pastor Perafan, the kingpin of the Bogota and El Cauca drug
cartel, who was arrested by Venezuelan soldiers in San Cristobal,
a border city with Colombia. 
